label: stop_id
comment: Stop ID/Stop name of the bus stops corresponding to the bus in this observation. SameAs: 'stop_id' field from GTFS Realtime message-Vehicleposition (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicleposition)

label: stop_sequence
comment: Sequence ID/sequence number for the current stop along the designated route. SameAs: 'current_stop_sequence' field from GTFS Realtime message-Vehicleposition  (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicleposition)
